### ================================================================================
### 🔄 订单状态更新
### ================================================================================

### 4.1 更新订单状态为已支付
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PAID"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.log("✅ 订单状态更新成功");
    } else {
        client.log("❌ 订单状态更新失败");
    }
%}

### 4.2 更新订单状态为已完成
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.log("✅ 订单状态更新成功");
    }
%}

